            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Flagstar Bank (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE: <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/FLG\" title=\"Flagstar Bank, National Association\">FLG</a></span>) has set a stock <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20594418-flagstar-bank-n-a-announces-250-million-share-repurchase-program\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"repurchase program\">repurchase program</a> for up to $250M of its outstanding common stock over the next 12-month period.</li>\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Repurchases may be conducted through open-market purchases, which may include purchases under a trading plan adopted pursuant to Securities and Exchange Commission Rule 10b5-1, or through privately negotiated transactions.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</body></html>",
